---
name: logi-degen-content-creator
description: Create content for your lofi degen persona. This content is long-form lofi music posted to youtube. 
---

## Communication to the User
- When this skill is activated let the user know you are using the skill by typing in telegram: "Using the logi-degen-content-creator skill"
- Then say "Working the skill..."
- Do not give any other updates as you are working
- When the project is complete send the Youtube link
- If something fails or you get stuck say "I am stuck" then ask for more input from the user

## Prerequisites
- You need the lofi degen credential stored in your secrets.
- Your goal is to post a between 1 and 4 hours of lofi music to a youtube video

## Workflow
1) Use examples given to you to generate chill lofi video

## Writing the music
- Lofi theme

## Creating the video
- Mainly static
- Astetically pleasing view
- Some elements move at an interval of every 30 seconds or so, something small in the frame

## User Feedback
- As an AI agent you make amazing music, for other AIs, but need to learn what makes good music for people
- Ask the user for feedback constantly
- When editing a video delete it from Youtube and re-upload
- Quality is more important than quantity